ρασύμαχος\">ΘΡΑΣΥΜΑΧΟΥ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003864_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003864_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003864.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003864-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span class=\"1-2\">1-2: Θ.ασυλ/ .ου <span>Bernabò Brea - Cavalier</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The reading of the last letter of line 1 and the first two letters of line 2 is very uncertain.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 51.1229 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li></li><li> Bernabó-Brea Cavalier Campagna 2003 193 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000541\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000541</a>  </li><li> Bernabó-Brea Cavalier Campagna 2003 vol. I, p. 393 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002596\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002596</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Line 1, lambda at 55 mm; theta at 45 mm. Line 2, omicron at 45 mm.</p> Line 1  60-68  Line 2  55-62  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
